  <thing id="pwDvlPvn6" name="Shielding Hellfire" description="{b}Effect:{/b} You enter the shielding hellfire stance. Until the stance ends, whenever you have any concealment, you gain a +4 power bonus to Stealth checks and resist 5 fire. If you already have fire resistance, increase that resistance by 5.\n{b}Infernal Pact:{/b} Whenever your Warlock&#146;s Curse is triggered, you gain a +4 power bonus to damage rolls with fire attack powers until the end of your next turn." compset="Power">
