  <thing id="pwDvlPwn10" name="Pit Fiend Harbinger" description="{b}Effect:{/b} Until the end of your next turn, you gain a +2 power bonus to AC, a fly speed equal to your speed, and fire resistance equal to 5 + your level (if you already have fire resistance, increase it by 5). While this effect persists, you cannot spend healing surges, and you must make an attack on your turn each round or take damage equal to your level at the end of your turn. This damage cannot be prevented or reduced in any way.\n{b}Sustain Minor:{/b} The effect persists until the end of your next turn.\n  {b}Infernal Pact:{/b} You gain 10 temporary hit points each time you sustain this power." compset="Power">
    <fieldval field="pwFlavor" value="Glorious pain rips through you as your skin blackens and hardens into devilish scales and great black wings, a crown of fire wreathing your brow."/>
