  <thing id="pwSnMshl1" name="Marshal&apos;s Interdiction" description="{b}Trigger:{/b} You hit an enemy with an attack.\n{b}Effect:{/b} The target is immobilized until the end of your next turn. You also mark the target until you end your turn without hitting or missing it with an attack. In addition, you designate the enemy as your marshal&#146;s quarry until the end of the encounter." compset="Power">
