  <thing id="pwSnMshl2" name="Marshal&apos;s Pursuit" description="{b}Effect:{/b} You assume the marshal&#146;s pursuit stance. Until the stance ends, you gain the following benefits.\nYou gain a +2 power bonus to speed.\nYou gain a +2 power bonus to all defenses against opportunity attacks that you provoke by moving.\nYou can shift 1 square as a free action at the end of each of your turns, but this movement must place you closer to or the same distance from your marshal&#146;s quarry." compset="Power">
