  <thing id="pwSklVrn2" name="Grace of the Masked Lord" description="{b}Effect:{/b} The burst creates a zone that lasts until the end of your next turn. While in the zone, you and each ally gain a +3 power bonus to all defenses against traps. In addition, each ally who starts his or her turn in the zone can make a saving throw against an effect caused by a trap that a save can end.\n{b}Sustain Minor:{/b} The zone persists until the end of your next turn." compset="Power">
