  <thing id="pwSklVrn10" name="Guise of the Faithful" description="{b}Effect:{/b} You transform the auditory, tactile, and visual qualities of the targets&#146; bodies and equipment. Each target assumes the appearance of a drow, and you can choose to provide a target with the appearance of a specific drow whom you have seen.\n    The illusion lasts for 1 hour, or you can end it as a minor action. A creature can recognize a target&#146;s form as illusory with an Insight check opposed by that target&#146;s Bluff check. The Bluff check is made with a +5 power bonus." compset="Power">
