  <thing id="pwTrpsmt1" name="Trip the Trap" description="{b}Requirement:{/b} You must have a trap-making kit on your person.\n{b}Trigger:{/b} An enemy enters a square adjacent to you.\n\n{b}Attack:{/b} Intelligence + 2 vs. Reflex\n    Level 11: Intelligence + 4 vs. Reflex\n    Level 21: Intelligence + 6 vs. Reflex\n\n{b}Hit:{/b} 1d6 + Intelligence modifier damage.\n    Level 11: 2d6 + Intelligence modifier damage.\n    Level 21: 3d6 + Intelligence modifier damage.\n\n{b}Effect:{/b} The target grants combat advantage until the end of your next turn." compset="Power">
