  <thing id="pwTuthn10b" name="Timeless Step" description="{b}Effect:{/b} You activate an aura 1 that lasts until the end of your next turn. Your melee weapon attacks and ranged weapon attacks against enemies in the aura gain the brutal 2 weapon property (against those enemies, reroll any weapon damage die that shows 1 or 2). In addition, any enemy that starts its turn in the aura is slowed until the end of your next turn.\n{b}Sustain Minor:{/b} The aura persists until the end of your next turn.\n{b}Special:{/b} You can use this power during an extended rest. If you do so, you require only 4 hours to gain the benefits of an extended rest." compset="Power">
