  <thing id="fTuathan1" name="Tuathan Starting Feature" description="You gain either Continue the Story or Shapechanger Physique.\n{b}Continue the Story{/b}\nYou gain a +1 bonus to death saving throws. In addition, whenever you make an Endurance check, you can roll twice and use either result.\n\n{b}Shapechanger&#146;s Physique{/b}\nWhenever you make an Athletics check, you can roll twice and use either result." compset="ThemeFeat">
