  <thing id="pwWrBear1b" name="Bear Shape Secondary Power" description="{b}Attack:{/b} Highest ability modifier + 3 vs. AC\n    Level 11: Highest ability modifier + 6\n    Level 21: Highest ability modifier + 9\n{b}Hit:{/b} 1d8 + highest ability modifier damage, and you mark the target until the start of your next turn.\n    Level 21: 2d8 + highest ability modifier damage.\n{b}Special:{/b} You can use this power in place of a melee basic attack." compset="Power">
