  <thing id="fWrWolf1" name="Werewolf Starting Feature" description="You gain a +2 power bonus to Intimidate checks.\n    You have the shapechanger subtype. As such, you are subject to effects that affect shapechangers. In addition, any enemy has combat advantage against you when attacking you with a silvered weapon or implement. Also, you are immune to moon frenzy.\n    Finally, you gain the wolf shape power." compset="ThemeFeat">
