  <thing id="fWrWolf5" name="Werewolf Level 5 Feature" description="When interacting with wolves and similar creatures, you gain a +2 bonus to Bluff, Diplomacy, or Intimidate checks.\n    In addition, while wolf shape is active, you gain a +2 power bonus to speed." compset="ThemeFeat">
