  <thing id="fWrWolf10" name="Werewolf Level 10 Feature" description="When you use the wolf shape power, you can assume the form of a humanoid-wolf hybrid, instead of a wolf. While in hybrid form, your equipment does not become part of your new form, and you are not forced to drop any items you are holding. You are also not limited to using implement and weapon attack powers that have the beast form keyword." compset="ThemeFeat">
